"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2pacx-1vqmf5bwqdkzxdpffrhytjp9ttk3ehb5qybt7strtnamlgtex0mjmeavxua47wan5ymb5fau7ymdbkqd/pubchart?oid=1880140124&format=image)\\n\\n```\\nOur annual award shows are broken and boring. Every year, there are deserving snubs and suspisious winners. Worst yet, selection committees are faceless Boards and organizations that don't represent the fans that they make choices for.\\n```\\n\\n![Rob Latour/REX/Shutterstock](https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/drake-2019-grammys.jpeg)\\n\\nThings have gotten so bad that Drake pulled out of the Grammys this year. I am used to artists complaining here and there, but if you make Drake quit, then we must go to war.\\n\\nI am proposing we create a DAO to take on the Grammys - let’s call it $AWARDZ for now. The goal of $AWARDZ is to democratize the music awards process. From selection of nominees to award winners to trophy design, I want to create a fairer process. Artists and fans alike, can move on from these annual squabbles and get to something that truly represents and rewards the best of the art form.\\n\\nThe key to this DAO will be equal representation for all involved. I believe that a 3-way split between fans, artists and media/influencers (with a little remaining for development) will lead to the best outcome.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/JHQDjxd91_MTpQog9sT-t.png?height=371&width=600)\\n\\nLet’s do this guys! This year has proved that crypto can do anything. PleasrDAO got its  hands on the mythical Wu Tang album….\\n\\n[https://beincrypto.com/pleasrdao-rescues-4-million-rare-wu-tang-album-mints-nft/](https://beincrypto.com/pleasrdao-rescues-4-million-rare-wu-tang-album-mints-nft/)\\n\\n… and we almost bought the Constitution for God’s sake;\\n\\n[https://news.artnet.com/market/sothebys-constitution-cryptocurrency-sale-2037156](https://news.artnet.com/market/sothebys-constitution-cryptocurrency-sale-2037156)\\n\\n[https://news.artnet.com/market/sothebys-constitution-cryptocurrency-sale-2037156](https://news.artnet.com/market/sothebys-constitution-cryptocurrency-sale-2037156)\\n\\nthe Grammy’s should be easy!\\n\\nMeet me on Discord:\\n\\n[https://discord.gg/uBf4xtzq](https://discord.gg/uBf4xtzq)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1639107894,\"title\":\"Screw the Grammys! Let's make our own\"},\"digest\":\"SpRo0iWmQK2m9MxT3QOX2vI4UoebGAkKqF5Rxfb8Fhg\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x71aB0BBD59156cd0623746971F4eb0067b6477Ad\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"1DbSEwUuquEWCcnzRUk7wF_dRT2NMMLFJMDYdMORtYk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"cpy51cCtr5V7IBcYF9ufUmT1E3ecmii1xkhdcYulY6g\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"1zVU9PyJ8KNgQTzIseaan6UJB_ooTvovhOjgazJ4L8N-3zEJ_7gbgIWLgXd4oL14VeQxDDWu3RzuYbhNjuO7dA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xf3f2bfb26f2322938ee2e09e08c6900a0f242ef5605ebf75e212a5928453218963c25f0c82cb050792efba92fb0355e539d34bc87e13854897103e9d5d447db91b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"1DbSEwUuquEWCcnzRUk7wF_dRT2NMMLFJMDYdMORtYk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"cpy51cCtr5V7IBcYF9ufUmT1E3ecmii1xkhdcYulY6g\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"LFPhHZOVTWZhZK_Y7SkTnCWX8wIQJLpkBscVs6rf2G8\"}"